WaitForThread (script event)
============================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type [Thread\_(scripting).html idThread], accessible via [Scripting\_basics.html\#sys sys] identifier.

Description
-----------

Waits for the given thread to terminate.

Usage
-----

*[Data\_types.html\#void void]* waitForThread( *[Data\_types.html\#float float]* **threadNumber** )

Parameters
----------

[threadNumber] - id of thread to wait for.

